00:13:33.572 --> 00:13:35.523
un zey hobn bakumen dem toyt.

00:13:36.728 --> 00:13:38.916
zenen arayngegangen tsu eynem,

00:13:39.968 --> 00:13:41.784
tsi er volt gevolt koyfn.

00:13:41.520 --> 00:13:42.796
a polyak?

00:13:42.499 --> 00:13:43.353
yo.

00:13:44.507 --> 00:13:46.846
aynvoyner in a dorf,

00:13:47.427 --> 00:13:50.149
du darfst hobn efsher aza kolner?

00:13:50.149 --> 00:13:52.112
vilst koyfn? zogt er, yo.

00:13:53.316 --> 00:13:58.609
zogt er ober, ikh hob nisht genug gelt, ikh vel arayngeyn tsum shokhn vel ikh borgn gelt, ikh vel im koyfn.

00:13:58.817 --> 00:14:01.581
fregt vifl, hot er gezogt azoy fil azoy fil,

00:14:01.581 --> 00:14:03.210
zogt er, vart do hinter,

00:14:03.210 --> 00:14:04.855
ikh vel arayngeyn tsum shokhn.

00:14:04.855 --> 00:14:07.333
ikh vel borgn gelt, ikh vel im koyfn.

00:14:08.622 --> 00:14:12.027
veyst vi azoy er hot gekoyft? er iz arayngekumen mit gever,

00:14:12.027 --> 00:14:13.610
un er hot zey geshosn.

00:14:13.853 --> 00:14:16.226
hot er gehat dem kolner far gornisht.

00:14:19.675 --> 00:14:21.221
er hot geshosn dayn f-

00:14:21.328 --> 00:14:22.790
dem kuzin,

00:14:22.932 --> 00:14:25.004
un mayn feter's eydem.

00:14:25.004 --> 00:14:27.415
tsvey. mit eyn mol.

00:14:27.437 --> 00:14:31.008
un mir zenen geven dentsmol bahaltn bay eynem vu men hot gehat

00:14:31.065 --> 00:14:36.074
aza a KRYJOWKA heyst es, vi azoy zogt men es a KRYJOWKA?

00:14:36.074 --> 00:14:38.012
aza baheltenish, unt-

00:14:38.119 --> 00:14:42.925
unter di khazeyrim, di khazeyrim hobn geven in der heykh un mir zenen gev-

00:14:42.925 --> 00:14:47.833
o in erd in erd azoy grobn der der m'hot im

00:14:43.333 --> 00:14:44.407
unter.

00:14:47.856 --> 00:14:50.550
m'hot im gedorfn batsoln,

00:14:50.708 --> 00:14:55.562
un er hot azoy gegrobn a grub un dort ze'mir geven bahaltn unter di khazeyrim.

00:14:55.888 --> 00:15:01.479
un dort eyner hot gedolt gedorfn kumen mit der kuzin, dos ze'mir shoyn geven ale tsuzamen mit di COUSINS.

00:15:01.479 --> 00:15:04.151
a baheltenish unter di khazeyrim.

00:15:04.579 --> 00:15:06.800
iz geven oysgegrobn a gro- a grub.

00:15:08.072 --> 00:15:16.486
un mir hobn gezen nokh a por te- heyst es, a por teg ze'mir dort geven, nisht mer, vos zey zenen gegangen farkoyfn, m'hot gedorfn gebn dem gelt,

00:15:18.450 --> 00:15:23.169
ven mir ho'mir gezen az zey zenen nishto, zenen nisht gekumen, ho'mir shoyn gevust

00:15:23.327 --> 00:15:25.869
az s'epes nisht gut.

00:15:25.977 --> 00:15:27.523
az zey lebn shoyn nisht.

00:15:28.322 --> 00:15:32.501
hot mayn feter gezogt, veyst vos? m'darf shoyn fun danet antloyfn.

00:15:33.587 --> 00:15:38.764
ze'mir bay di nakht a- aroys, heyst es, far togs iz shoyn geven, nisht bay der nakht,

00:15:38.764 --> 00:15:40.432
s'hot shoyn ongehoybn tsu togn,

00:15:40.455 --> 00:15:42.946
ze'mir aroys un avek in a vald arayn.

00:15:43.662 --> 00:15:45.186
dos iz geven

00:15:45.186 --> 00:15:48.094
du bist ge- an- antloyfn, dayn feter?

00:15:46.041 --> 00:15:50.355
i- i- ikh, mayn feter, mayn bruder,

00:15:50.665 --> 00:15:51.671
un Nome.

00:15:56.470 --> 00:15:59.451
dents- dentsmolt iz shoyn Nome nisht gevezn.

00:16:00.047 --> 00:16:01.813
vos iz geshen mit Nome?

00:16:01.617 --> 00:16:03.214
vos iz geshen mit Nomen?

00:16:03.861 --> 00:16:06.203
zi hot dort gehat a bakante,

00:16:06.203 --> 00:16:07.854
a a shiksl,

00:16:07.962 --> 00:16:10.338
velkhes zi hot ir gekent oykh fun di SCHOOL.

00:16:10.338 --> 00:16:11.870
yene hot bakumen

00:16:11.961 --> 00:16:17.793
a m'hot gelozt ir visn, zi hot bakumen az zi dorf tsu der arbet keyn Doytshland.

00:16:18.913 --> 00:16:22.012
vi azoy zogt men es, aza min,

00:16:24.887 --> 00:16:26.285
a zi darf forn.

00:16:26.285 --> 00:16:29.640
zey- fun fun zey hot men oykh genumen fun zeyere tsu der arbet.

00:16:29.764 --> 00:16:32.593
nor zey hot men nisht geshosn, zey hobn gut gelebt.

00:16:33.426 --> 00:16:35.597
hot mayn shvester gezogt tsun ir,

00:16:36.717 --> 00:16:38.094
veyst vos?

00:16:39.113 --> 00:16:41.672
ikh ken forn far dir az du vilst,

00:16:41.982 --> 00:16:43.444
un du kenst zayn in shtub.

00:16:43.635 --> 00:16:45.117
voltst gevolt?

00:16:45.117 --> 00:16:46.818
hot zi zikh gefreyt, zogt zi, yo.

00:16:47.837 --> 00:16:49.653
un m'hot gedorfn aroyf klebn

00:16:50.200 --> 00:16:53.046
a a PICTURE oyf dem

00:16:53.052 --> 00:16:56.269
onvayzung fun di doytshn vos hobn zey geshikt,

00:16:56.882 --> 00:16:59.171
un un zi hot dokh nisht gehat keyn PICTURE,

00:17:00.460 --> 00:17:02.445
iz zi geganen

00:17:02.704 --> 00:17:04.132
un zi hot zikh gemakht,

00:17:04.257 --> 00:17:06.208
zi hot zikh gelozt fotografirn,

00:17:06.737 --> 00:17:08.655
a shteyger azoy vi haynt,

00:17:08.964 --> 00:17:13.632
un oyfn tsveytn tog hot zi gedorfn geyn aroysnemen di PICTURE,

00:17:15.073 --> 00:17:20.782
un geyn tsu di az zi zol zikh untershraybn tsi vi azoy, un zi hot gezo- gedorfn

00:17:20.782 --> 00:17:22.627
forn keyn Doytshland far ir

00:17:23.156 --> 00:17:24.466
tsu der arbet.

00:17:25.030 --> 00:17:27.471
ven zi iz gegangen oyfn tsveytn tog

00:17:27.814 --> 00:17:29.613
aroysnemen di PICTURE,

00:17:30.227 --> 00:17:34.034
un nokh kumen tsu undz, mir zenen dentsmol geven shoyn an andere ort,

00:17:34.547 --> 00:17:36.329
oyf a shtal-boydem,

00:17:37.129 --> 00:17:39.131
vos keyner hot nisht gevust.

00:17:39.238 --> 00:17:41.021
m'iz arayngekrokhn,

00:17:41.078 --> 00:17:43.080
un m'iz dort gezesn,

00:17:43.339 --> 00:17:45.648
on gornisht, m'hot moyre gehat tsu zogn.

00:17:45.648 --> 00:17:50.521
mir hobn gelebt az keyner hot undz nisht getort zen, nisht mir hobn getort vemenen zen.

00:17:51.692 --> 00:17:55.550
un u- un un ven mir hobn gezen az zi iz nishto,

00:17:55.607 --> 00:17:57.086
hot men shoyn gevust,

00:17:57.143 --> 00:17:59.162
mayn shvester iz nisht gekumen,

00:17:59.185 --> 00:18:02.199
hot men shoyn gezen az der brokh iz fartik.

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:06.974
iz oyf tsu morgns in der fri, mayn feter iz aro-,

00:18:07.133 --> 00:18:10.277
oyfn tsveytn tog bay der nakht, mayn shve- mayn

00:18:10.277 --> 00:18:15.091
mayn feter iz aropgegangen, tsugegangen dortn in dorf arayn betn a shtikl broyt,

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:17.961
ir hot efsher epes tsu esn,

00:18:18.439 --> 00:18:19.682
hot gehert,

00:18:20.076 --> 00:18:22.097
hot men im shoyn gezogt di psure,

00:18:22.097 --> 00:18:24.710
veyst vos? az m'hot do yetst geshosn

00:18:28.277 --> 00:18:29.503
a meydl,

00:18:32.007 --> 00:18:34.313
ver hot geshosn? a POLICEMAN.

00:18:34.656 --> 00:18:38.177
un der der POLICEMAN, ikh gedenk nisht haynt dem nomen,

00:18:38.520 --> 00:18:41.039
um sof hot geven der POLICEMAN

00:18:41.039 --> 00:18:43.424
ver hot flegt tsu undz in shtub arayn araynkumen

00:18:43.785 --> 00:18:46.178
esn, trinken, m'hot geflegt im gebn

00:18:46.178 --> 00:18:49.347
fun di yagd hot men geflegt gebn im fleysh aheym,

00:18:50.147 --> 00:18:52.464
zayn froy iz geven a TEACHERin,

00:18:52.464 --> 00:18:54.393
un un mayn shvester

00:18:54.940 --> 00:18:58.410
iz geven in di SCHOOL vu zayn vu zayn vayb

00:18:59.125 --> 00:19:00.860
hot geleyent,

00:19:00.860 --> 00:19:01.936
hot gelernt.

00:19:03.900 --> 00:19:05.244
shtel zikh for!

00:19:06.567 --> 00:19:08.383
un er hot ir geshisn.

00:19:08.372 --> 00:19:09.904
un er hot ir geshosn.

00:19:09.904 --> 00:19:12.467
mir ven mir zenen aroys oyf der fray,

00:19:14.076 --> 00:19:15.707
mir hobn im gezukht,

00:19:16.135 --> 00:19:18.272
mir hobn gevust vu er voynt,

00:19:18.278 --> 00:19:19.959
mir hobn gevust zayn nomen,

00:19:20.134 --> 00:19:22.676
ober mir hobn im shoyn nisht gefunen.

00:19:22.783 --> 00:19:25.460
ikh gloyb az er iz ergets antlofn.

00:19:27.188 --> 00:19:30.202
SO iz geven dir,

00:19:30.242 --> 00:19:32.818
dayn feter un dayn bruder.

00:19:34.326 --> 00:19:35.872
fun di nenste.

00:19:36.486 --> 00:19:38.674
bist geven in di velder den.

00:19:38.713 --> 00:19:41.137
ikh bin geven vu ikh hob nor gekent.

00:19:40.992 --> 00:19:44.681
gedenkstu di nemener fun di shtetlekh

00:19:45.244 --> 00:19:46.908
ts- vu du bist geven?

00:19:47.691 --> 00:19:49.744
di FARMS.

00:19:48.602 --> 00:19:50.250
di farmS,

00:19:50.256 --> 00:19:52.412
di farmS, yo ikh ikh bin ge-

00:19:52.412 --> 00:19:53.557
ikh gedenk.

00:19:53.901 --> 00:19:55.177
zo-

00:19:55.437 --> 00:19:57.726
ikh gedenk, ikh hob zey farshribn afile.

00:19:58.356 --> 00:20:01.033
dos iz gevezn

00:20:01.866 --> 00:20:04.323
eyn PLACE iz geven Kubyasi,

00:20:04.650 --> 00:20:06.031
vos s'hot geheysn,

00:20:06.031 --> 00:20:10.821
un Rotshadi, Bilani, Dmokhi,

00:20:12.092 --> 00:20:14.583
ikh vel dir bald dertseyln fun Dmokhi,

00:20:14.623 --> 00:20:16.760
vos iz geven, in dem Dmokhi.

00:20:16.665 --> 00:20:18.464
dos iz geven der dritn?

00:20:18.336 --> 00:20:19.359
dos d-

00:20:19.382 --> 00:20:23.341
un un nakher iz geven Bilani vu mir zenen oykhet gevezn.

00:20:23.854 --> 00:20:27.690
nor Dmokhi, do ho'mir gehat a umglik.

00:20:27.690 --> 00:20:30.784
dos iz mayn bruder gevorn adurkh geshosn

00:20:30.874 --> 00:20:33.551
un mayn feter hot men geshosn oyf toyt.

00:20:35.262 --> 00:20:37.314
do hot zikh ongehoybn di tsores.

00:20:37.455 --> 00:20:38.951
frishe tsores.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:40.858
un mir hot men gekhapt.

00:20:42.776 --> 00:20:45.096
mir zenen geven bay eynemen,

00:20:45.096 --> 00:20:47.489
un mayn feter hot im gekent gut.

00:20:48.306 --> 00:20:51.492
er iz a mol geshtanen shoyn dort a por

00:20:51.492 --> 00:20:53.261
a por vokhn afile.

00:20:53.402 --> 00:20:56.518
iz er gegangen er hot zokh gevolt nokh a mol geyn,

00:20:56.777 --> 00:20:58.931
efsher ken men vider dort zayn.

00:21:00.777 --> 00:21:06.418
iz men dort aroyf gekrokhn, er hot nisht gevust, oyfn bay der nakht, nor bay der nakht,

00:21:06.418 --> 00:21:07.655
in der fri,

00:21:07.932 --> 00:21:09.025
ven der

00:21:09.025 --> 00:21:14.101
ven der balbos iz arayngekumen UNK, er iz gegangen gebn di beheymes tsu esn,

00:21:14.293 --> 00:21:16.467
im hot mayn feter gezogt,

00:21:16.467 --> 00:21:17.859
gelozt zikh hern.

00:21:17.859 --> 00:21:20.463
az mir zenen gekumen, mir viln dir

00:21:20.470 --> 00:21:24.010
fregn efsher ken men nokh zayn bay dir a tsayt,

00:21:24.010 --> 00:21:25.504
oy do iz do mayn

00:21:25.504 --> 00:21:27.281
mayn bruder's

00:21:28.165 --> 00:21:30.353
mayn bruder's tokhter,

00:21:30.409 --> 00:21:32.101
iz oyf mir, un mayn

00:21:32.777 --> 00:21:35.786
un mayn bruder's zun.

00:21:37.935 --> 00:21:39.987
git er a zog,

00:21:40.382 --> 00:21:42.438
ikh vil adurkh redn mit mayn vayb.

00:21:42.438 --> 00:21:43.498
zogt er, gut.

00:21:43.707 --> 00:21:45.135
zog- zogt er,

00:21:45.478 --> 00:21:49.247
ikh hob a bite, dos iz geven fun shabes oyf zuntik ze'mir a-

00:21:49.247 --> 00:21:51.480
aroyfgegangen, dos gedenk ikh.

00:21:53.157 --> 00:22:00.289
zo- zogt er azoy, veyst vos, ikh hob a bite, efsher kenstu undz epes aroyfbrengen esn, mir zenen zeyer hungerik.

00:22:00.801 --> 00:22:02.887
zogt er, gut, ikh vel zogn mayn vayb.

00:22:03.214 --> 00:22:07.528
hot er gegebn di beheymes tsu esn dos ershte, nakher iz arayngegangen

00:22:07.973 --> 00:22:11.274
un mir vartn un vartn un do

00:22:13.137 --> 00:22:18.227
un di kishkes moln zikh, un s'gornisht do afile a b- bisl vaser nisht.

00:22:18.267 --> 00:22:20.016
m'hot zikh koym dervart,

00:22:20.157 --> 00:22:23.273
hot er gebrengt a shtikl broyt mit milkh,

00:22:23.633 --> 00:22:24.538
geven gut.

00:22:24.561 --> 00:22:26.495
ales iz gut geven yene tsayt.

00:22:27.750 --> 00:22:29.144
un zogt er azoy,

00:22:29.657 --> 00:22:33.785
veyst vos, mayn vayb hot moyre ir zolt do zayn.

00:22:33.842 --> 00:22:36.164
un kh'hob nisht genug shtroy dort,

00:22:36.458 --> 00:22:39.422
un mayn vayb iz zeyer moyredik, veyst dokh,

00:22:39.782 --> 00:22:45.058
az yetst oyb m'gefint vemenen vert mayn gantse mishpokhe volt men oysgeharget.

00:22:45.418 --> 00:22:47.904
hot mayn feter gezogt, veyst vos,

00:22:47.904 --> 00:22:50.913
az du host azoy moyre veln mir avekgeyn oyf der nakht.

00:22:50.937 --> 00:22:52.433
mir zayn ibern tog.

00:22:54.784 --> 00:23:00.498
un zogt er, un mir geyn yetst, dervayl hot ir tsu esn, mir geyn yetst

00:23:00.808 --> 00:23:02.287
tsu di CHURCH.

00:23:03.407 --> 00:23:04.481
her azoy,

00:23:05.348 --> 00:23:09.679
un ven m'vet kumen, vet men dir epes aroyfbrengen vider. nu gut.

00:23:12.216 --> 00:23:14.302
do heybt zikh on di tsores.

00:23:15.186 --> 00:23:18.352
ven er iz avekgegangen in di CHURCH vi er hot gezogt,

00:23:19.590 --> 00:23:22.841
UNK iz er avekgegangen, er hot zikh opgeshmuest

00:23:23.050 --> 00:23:26.132
mit di andere banditn azelkhe,

00:23:28.011 --> 00:23:31.262
az az mir veln di nakht aropgeyn,

00:23:31.673 --> 00:23:33.472
zol men undz avek shisn.

00:23:35.858 --> 00:23:38.214
nor mir hobn dokh nisht gevust gornisht,

00:23:38.946 --> 00:23:40.495
s'gekumen oyf der nakht,

00:23:40.495 --> 00:23:43.175
hot er undz epes dort aroyfgebrengt nakher esn,

00:23:43.215 --> 00:23:46.111
un mir hobn shoyn gevart bay der nakht m'zol aropgeyn.

00:23:46.810 --> 00:23:50.043
un dos iz geven zumer.

00:23:50.860 --> 00:23:52.204
s'geven azoy

00:23:53.070 --> 00:23:55.376
s'gevaksn di tvue,

00:23:55.433 --> 00:23:57.058
JULY, AUGUST,

00:23:57.058 --> 00:23:58.408
azoy in di tsayt

00:23:58.408 --> 00:23:59.598
azoy vi yetst.

00:23:59.598 --> 00:24:02.464
azoy gloybn ikh, azoy o vi s'gevaksn di tvue.

00:24:02.537 --> 00:24:04.927
mir hobn dentsmolt nisht gevust a tog

00:24:05.068 --> 00:24:07.545
ven, vos, der datum,

00:24:07.545 --> 00:24:08.943
mir hobn gelebt

00:24:09.000 --> 00:24:10.799
nokh erger vi khayes.

00:24:10.806 --> 00:24:13.550
ikh hob mir, ikh hob mekane geven a hunt,

00:24:14.350 --> 00:24:15.604
a kats,

00:24:15.604 --> 00:24:20.067
zey hobn gehat khotsh ver zol zey aroysbrengen epes esn, tsu arayn rufn, tsu

00:24:20.067 --> 00:24:23.574
tsu ton a red tsu zey, tsi vos, ober nisht tsu undz.

00:24:29.892 --> 00:24:32.147
bay der nakht zogt mayn feter,

00:24:33.013 --> 00:24:34.081
nu, m'darf

00:24:34.081 --> 00:24:37.091
shoyn aropgeyn, s'shoyn genug shpet.

00:24:39.223 --> 00:24:41.680
iz er aropgegangen der ershter,

00:24:42.278 --> 00:24:44.145
mayn bruder,

00:24:44.286 --> 00:24:46.288
un ikh bin gegangen arop

00:24:46.378 --> 00:24:49.511
di di drite, undz ze'mir geven nor dray dentsmolt.

00:24:50.563 --> 00:24:53.564
un ven m'iz aroys, aropgegangen, un mayn feter hot

00:24:53.564 --> 00:24:58.590
er iz dokh geven a hoykher, hot er mir geholfn aropgeyn, ikh hob mir aropgelozt,

00:24:59.102 --> 00:25:01.306
un er hot mir gedorfn

00:25:01.870 --> 00:25:03.385
onnemen aroplozn.

00:25:03.385 --> 00:25:04.912
azoy vi er nemt mir on,

00:25:04.912 --> 00:25:06.942
aro- aroptsulozn,

00:25:07.253 --> 00:25:08.850
tut men a geshrey oyf

00:25:09.025 --> 00:25:10.099
oyf poylish,

00:25:11.252 --> 00:25:12.613
"di hent aroyf!"

00:25:14.813 --> 00:25:17.152
oyf Poylish, "RECE DO GORY!" azoy o.

00:25:19.183 --> 00:25:23.750
az mayn feter hot derhert, hot er shoyn ongehoybn tsu loyfn. er hot gevust vu er loyft ober

00:25:23.773 --> 00:25:27.294
un un mayn bruder hot ongehoybn tsu loyfn, ober ikh hob nisht gevust

00:25:27.823 --> 00:25:29.065
vu tsu loyfn.

00:25:29.967 --> 00:25:31.091
hob ikh

00:25:31.266 --> 00:25:32.604
geton do a

00:25:32.604 --> 00:25:39.312
epes bin ikh a-, s'geven fintster, hob ikh a- ongehoybn tsu antloyfn azoy oyf bay di shtal, dort vu s'do gendz, hiner, ikh veys vos,

00:25:39.312 --> 00:25:41.385
un zey hobn mit BATTERIES

00:25:41.998 --> 00:25:45.294
zey hobn gelozt un zey hobn mir gefunen, zey hobn mir shoyn ongenumen

00:25:45.294 --> 00:25:47.226
bay di hent, un m'firt mir shoyn.
